Privacy Policy for Neon Dodge

Neon Drift does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.
The app does not use analytics, advertising, or third-party tracking
services, and it does not require an account or internet connection
to play. Your high score is saved locally on your device only, using
Apple's standard UserDefaults storage, and is never sent anywhere.

